  !SIDEWAYS! ASCII Tetris game
=================================

I forked and modified Gregwar's game
because I wanted to run it on a 20x4
character display. If you want to
run this on anything other than a
20x4 character display, go and get
Gregwar's version. It is better
for what you want. Otherwise,
dive in!


 To compile, use:

 make

 It will output a binary file Tetris.

 Controls:

  j:    left
  k:    rotate
  l:    right
  [space]:    bottom (quicker)

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
!                                        !
!O X # # & &   X Z Z     X   O O & & X   !
!X X X #   & X X X Z Z X X X O     & X X !
!O         &                 O     & X   !
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
